We have following
cars, motorbikes.

00:50:01.790 --> 00:50:03.415
There are only going
to about 30 people

00:50:03.415 --> 00:50:06.390
on it, 30, 35 people on
it, fully-guided motorbikes

00:50:06.390 --> 00:50:09.589
and ride captains,
lovely hotels.

00:50:09.589 --> 00:50:10.880
So we're looking forward to it.

00:50:10.880 --> 00:50:13.380
And hopefully we will
have some names on it

00:50:13.380 --> 00:50:17.820
as well, where we haven't
got full agreements yet

00:50:17.820 --> 00:50:20.850
from the likes of
Indurain, Delgado.

00:50:20.850 --> 00:50:22.530
I'm trying to get
Delgado to come back.

00:50:22.530 --> 00:50:25.980
And we lit the stage.

00:50:25.980 --> 00:50:28.140
But this time, not collapsing.

00:50:28.140 --> 00:50:30.570
And for the fun of it,
so it'll be a few names

00:50:30.570 --> 00:50:33.750
that'll be coming along with
us, either for three days

00:50:33.750 --> 00:50:34.904
or for one of the days.

00:50:34.904 --> 00:50:36.570
Even Eddie Merckx
we're talking to also.

00:50:36.570 --> 00:50:38.100
Maybe he might
come along and ride

00:50:38.100 --> 00:50:39.808
that, at the last few
kilometers with us.

00:50:39.808 --> 00:50:40.710
So we're doing that.

00:50:40.710 --> 00:50:41.870
And also, we have
a lighthouse tour

00:50:41.870 --> 00:50:43.995
at the end of the year,
which is in Mallorca, which

00:50:43.995 --> 00:50:45.560
is four days around the island.

00:50:45.560 --> 00:50:47.720
Every day, changing
hotels for four days.

00:50:47.720 --> 00:50:50.127
Which is something we've done
for the last two years now.

00:50:50.127 --> 00:50:51.460
And that's been a great success.

00:50:51.460 --> 00:50:54.466
So the cycling
holidays are booming.

00:50:54.466 --> 00:50:56.090
There are many guys
out there doing it.

00:50:56.090 --> 00:50:58.770
I was one of the first
guys doing it 21 years ago.

00:50:58.770 --> 00:51:01.160
Now there's hundreds
of them doing it now.

00:51:01.160 --> 00:51:02.250
But we're still there.

